    </ul>
    <p>This information is used to compile statistical information about the use of our Site. It is not used for any
      other purpose. If you do not want 'cookies' to be used, please disable them via your browser settings.</p>

    <h3>Links to other websites</h3>
    <p>Our Site may contain links to third party websites, and similarly, third party websites may also have links to
      our Site. If you follow a link to any of these other websites, kindly note that these websites have their own
      privacy policies and that we do not accept any responsibility or liability for your access to these websites.
      Please check their individual privacy policies for more information on how your data or any other data is handled
      by these websites.</p>
  </section>

